<br>
What my sugestion would be is like the plane of Hate, Fear and Air. PoG get its own section, now as I stated this is not a reservable plane, but at least it would help with signing up for the plane =). Title it as POG Intensions and not scheduling POG, and everyone knows what ever raid is up on there is not a reservation but merely an intention to few the plane, but at least we will have somewhere to get out that we wish to attend a raid in the zone, and we could have some place to stage a meeting place and time and at least have a list.<br>
<br>
Remember this is just an idea and I would like to see others comments and suggestions to this, please feel free to respond =) <p><BR>
